meta.bio:
Eric is a Creative Director at BPD with 20+ years of experience leading award-winning campaigns across top agencies in New York, California, Colorado, Oregon, and London. Known for his bold thinking and sharp storytelling, Eric brings a strategic, collaborative approach to solving complex brand challenges. Eric blends creativity with leadership to consistently deliver standout work that ignites greatness.

Eric is an avid triathlete who thrives on maintaining a strong balance between body and mind—believing both should be stretched and challenged every day. He’s built a full and joyful life with his two children (ages 9 and 10), his partner, and her son.

&nbsp;

